  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="DA">Creating structures for rural youth leader&#x2019;s mobilization, capacitating, and mentoring for more effective execution of their policy making and development roles within the Uganda Local Government system &#x2013; a pilot in Yumbe and Mayuge districts.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="DA">Our project&#x2019;s overall aim is to pilot and develop a grassroots based structure for mobilization, capacitating, mentoring and long-term motivation of youth leaders and youth policy makers at the lower local government level (parish &amp; sub county) in Uganda, in understanding how; Local Governments operate, what their roles as leaders in this system are, understanding processes around budget allocations, decision making, and how one gets youth issues into the decision/policy agenda, as well as advocacy for &amp; influence of policy.</narrative>
  </description>
